  "text": "We have developed a risk calculator (Fig 1) which incorporates the important clinical parameters associated with grade progression in a surveillance cohort [CITATION_1] . Note that, based on simple clinical factors, a patient's likelihood of upgrading varies from 10 to 70 %.",
